videos.headline: Mizzou scores unconventional TD on defense
videos.description: Ryan Hilinski catches his own batted pass and throws it backwards to the ground where it is ruled a fumble and recovered by Missouri's Cale Garrett in the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mizzou scores unconventional TD on defense) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bryant throws 21-yard INT
videos.description: Missouri's Kelly Bryant throws an interception to South Carolina's D.J. Wonnum who returns it 21 yards to the Missouri one yard line.

videos.headline: Bryant finds Okwuegbunam for Mizzou TD
videos.description: Kelly Bryant completes a pass to a wide-open Albert Okwuegbunam who trots into the end zone for an easy three-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bryant finds Okwuegbunam for Mizzou TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Badie races 21 yards for Mizzou TD
videos.description: Kelly Bryant completes a short pass to Tyler Badie who takes off to score a 21-yard Missouri touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Badie races 21 yards for Mizzou TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hilinski throws 100-yard pick-6
videos.description: Ryan Hilinski's pass is intercepted by Ronnell Perkins who returns it 100 yards for a Mizzou touchdown.
